									We will diagnose your condition, provide advise, and prescribe medication & other products as required.
								</p>
								<hr class="border_transparent">
								<h2><span><i>3</i></span>Get Reminders & Follow-up</h2>
								<p class="bullet_pad">
									We will provide you customised dailty reminders for what to do, and an extra follow-up consultaiton, to ensure your treatment provides the best possible result.
